5
00:00:11.970 --> 00:00:14.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What, and let the Jerries</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>cross the Channel? Never.</c.bg_transparent>

6
00:00:14.639 --> 00:00:16.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is sort of a shame</c.bg_transparent>
