7
00:00:17.642 --> 00:00:20.061 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Wish we didn't have to.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's like a sculpture</c.bg_transparent>

8
00:00:20.145 --> 00:00:22.188 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>a monument to your year as a bachelor.</c.bg_transparent>

9
00:00:22.272 --> 00:00:23.606 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, I suppose it is.</c.bg_transparent>

10
00:00:23.857 --> 00:00:25.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who are we to dismantle this piece of art?</c.bg_transparent>

11
00:00:26.151 --> 00:00:27.110 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know.</c.bg_transparent>

12
00:00:27.902 --> 00:00:29.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But if we don't, Keiko'll dismantle me.</c.bg_transparent>

13
00:00:48.923 --> 00:00:50.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Daddy.</c.bg_transparent>

14
00:00:50.800 --> 00:00:52.135 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hi, sweetie.</c.bg_transparent>

15
00:00:52.385 --> 00:00:53.219 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh!</c.bg_transparent>

16
00:00:57.307 --> 00:00:58.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hi.</c.bg_transparent>

17
00:01:06.149 --> 00:01:08.735 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The one good thing about going away</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is coming home.</c.bg_transparent>

18
00:01:09.319 --> 00:01:11.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I never want to be apart like that again.</c.bg_transparent>

19
00:01:11.863 --> 00:01:15.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Daddy, Daddy! I have a little brother</c.bg_transparent>

20
00:01:15.950 --> 00:01:18.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Really? Is that him?</c.bg_transparent>

21
00:01:19.537 --> 00:01:20.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. He's in there.</c.bg_transparent>

22
00:01:23.166 --> 00:01:24.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Surprise.</c.bg_transparent>

23
00:01:26.878 --> 00:01:27.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A baby?</c.bg_transparent>

24
00:01:29.255 --> 00:01:33.593 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeah. I--I thought you'd be happy.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I mean, we talked about it</c.bg_transparent>

25
00:01:33.676 --> 00:01:35.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and decided we'd start trying.</c.bg_transparent>

26
00:01:35.887 --> 00:01:39.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I know.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We--We--Well, but your last visit,</c.bg_transparent>

27
00:01:40.058 --> 00:01:41.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>you were only here the one night, and...</c.bg_transparent>

28
00:01:42.560 --> 00:01:44.604 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought it'd take a couple of nights.</c.bg_transparent>

29
00:01:45.146 --> 00:01:48.900 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To be honest... a lot more nights.</c.bg_transparent>

30
00:01:49.776 --> 00:01:51.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess we just got lucky this time.</c.bg_transparent>

31
00:01:54.239 --> 00:01:55.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess so.</c.bg_transparent>

32
00:02:03.164 --> 00:02:05.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Vedek Porta.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Nerys.</c.bg_transparent>

33
00:02:06.084 --> 00:02:11.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So, this is where you are</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when you're not at the Temple.</c.bg_transparent>

34
00:02:14.008 --> 00:02:15.093 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Very impressive.</c.bg_transparent>

35
00:02:15.635 --> 00:02:17.011 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Haven't you ever been to Ops?</c.bg_transparent>

36
00:02:17.303 --> 00:02:22.016 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What business would an old monk have here,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>except maybe helping a young couple</c.bg_transparent>

37
00:02:22.100 --> 00:02:23.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to meet the Emissary?</c.bg_transparent>

38
00:02:25.061 --> 00:02:26.479 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you sure this is a good time?</c.bg_transparent>

39
00:02:27.230 --> 00:02:28.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think he'll be able to fit you in.</c.bg_transparent>

40
00:02:28.982 --> 00:02:30.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you so much for doing this, Major.</c.bg_transparent>

41
00:02:31.025 --> 00:02:32.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I'm glad to.</c.bg_transparent>

42
00:02:35.280 --> 00:02:36.739 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They can take the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Rubicon.</i></c.bg_transparent>

43
00:02:36.823 --> 00:02:37.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door chimes )</c.bg_transparent>

44
00:02:38.199 --> 00:02:39.784 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come in.</c.bg_transparent>

45
00:02:40.827 --> 00:02:41.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Vedek Porta's here</c.bg_transparent>

46
00:02:41.911 --> 00:02:43.496 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>with the young couple</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that just got married.</c.bg_transparent>

47
00:02:43.997 --> 00:02:45.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're hoping</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to get the Emissary's blessing.</c.bg_transparent>

48
00:02:46.958 --> 00:02:47.917 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bring them in.</c.bg_transparent>

49
00:02:51.296 --> 00:02:53.214 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You remember the words?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The marriage blessing?</c.bg_transparent>

50
00:02:53.298 --> 00:02:54.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Mm-hmm.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I think so.</c.bg_transparent>

51
00:02:57.677 --> 00:03:00.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Emissary, we're very grateful to you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for seeing us.</c.bg_transparent>

52
00:03:01.264 --> 00:03:02.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not at all.</c.bg_transparent>

53
00:03:02.849 --> 00:03:04.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, if you'll just join hands...</c.bg_transparent>

54
00:03:08.062 --> 00:03:11.482 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Zhia'kala, tar'eh anu suur...</i></c.bg_transparent>

55
00:03:12.150 --> 00:03:14.903 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>te'von, aka'lu rez... ka'vor</i></c.bg_transparent>

56
00:03:15.236 --> 00:03:16.195 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>mat'ana kel.</i></c.bg_transparent>

57
00:03:17.196 --> 00:03:18.239 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

58
00:03:18.323 --> 00:03:19.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you very much.</c.bg_transparent>

59
00:03:24.871 --> 00:03:27.582 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your accent is getting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>much better, Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

60
00:03:27.957 --> 00:03:29.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm glad to hear it.</c.bg_transparent>

61
00:03:32.587 --> 00:03:34.255 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighing )</c.bg_transparent>

62
00:03:34.881 --> 00:03:37.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It isn't that bad, is it,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>being the Emissary?</c.bg_transparent>

63
00:03:39.302 --> 00:03:41.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A few ceremonies, an occasional blessing.</c.bg_transparent>

64
00:03:42.639 --> 00:03:43.848 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't say it was that bad.</c.bg_transparent>

65
00:03:43.932 --> 00:03:47.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's just hard getting used</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to being a religious icon.</c.bg_transparent>

66
00:03:47.685 --> 00:03:50.188 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-DAX: Really?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I think I'd like it.</c.bg_transparent>

67
00:03:50.480 --> 00:03:51.773 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Kira to Sisko.</i></c.bg_transparent>

68
00:03:52.315 --> 00:03:54.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-You'd better get out here.</i></c.bg_transparent>

69
00:03:54.651 --> 00:03:56.027 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>There's something</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>coming through the wormhole.</i></c.bg_transparent>

70
00:04:10.208 --> 00:04:11.042 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A lightship.</c.bg_transparent>

71
00:04:11.125 --> 00:04:12.210 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: I don't know where it came from.</c.bg_transparent>

72
00:04:12.293 --> 00:04:14.754 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>According to remote sensors,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it never entered the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

73
00:04:14.837 --> 00:04:17.340 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>From these readings, I'd say that ship's</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about 300 years old.</c.bg_transparent>

74
00:04:17.423 --> 00:04:18.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Life signs?</c.bg_transparent>

75
00:04:18.967 --> 00:04:20.301 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's someone on board,</c.bg_transparent>

76
00:04:20.385 --> 00:04:22.011 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-a Bajoran.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Try hailing them.</c.bg_transparent>

77
00:04:23.388 --> 00:04:24.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: No response.</c.bg_transparent>

78
00:04:25.098 --> 00:04:27.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: Whoever's in there could be injured.</c.bg_transparent>

79
00:04:28.268 --> 00:04:30.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tractor the ship into transporter range</c.bg_transparent>

80
00:04:30.228 --> 00:04:32.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and beam the passenger</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>directly into the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>

81
00:04:37.402 --> 00:04:39.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( moaning )</c.bg_transparent>

82
00:04:42.824 --> 00:04:44.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's a little disoriented.</c.bg_transparent>

83
00:04:46.953 --> 00:04:49.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm Captain Benjamin Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

84
00:04:49.580 --> 00:04:52.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're aboard a Federation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>space station near Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

85
00:04:52.667 --> 00:04:54.836 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is Kira Nerys, my First Officer.</c.bg_transparent>

86
00:04:58.006 --> 00:04:59.090 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who are you?</c.bg_transparent>

87
00:05:01.134 --> 00:05:02.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am the Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

88
00:07:06.050 --> 00:07:10.513 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was headed back to Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>My lightship was caught in an ion storm.</c.bg_transparent>

89
00:07:11.514 --> 00:07:13.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>It nearly tore it apart.</c.bg_transparent>

90
00:07:14.559 --> 00:07:18.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>A girder came loose from the bulkhead</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and impaled me through the shoulder, here.</c.bg_transparent>

91
00:07:19.021 --> 00:07:22.608 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I remember thinking I was going to die</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>alone in space</c.bg_transparent>

92
00:07:23.234 --> 00:07:26.487 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>when a strange opening</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>appeared in the sky.</c.bg_transparent>

93
00:07:27.029 --> 00:07:32.493 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>AKOREM: I was terrified at first,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and then, I realized what was happening.</c.bg_transparent>

94
00:07:34.245 --> 00:07:38.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets were opening the gates</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the Celestial Temple</c.bg_transparent>

95
00:07:39.709 --> 00:07:41.043 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>and drawing me to them.</c.bg_transparent>

96
00:07:42.378 --> 00:07:43.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>What happened then?</c.bg_transparent>

97
00:07:43.921 --> 00:07:45.381 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>AKOREM: It's difficult to describe.</c.bg_transparent>

98
00:07:45.882 --> 00:07:51.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>They took the form of people that I know,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>my grandfather, my brother,</c.bg_transparent>

99
00:07:52.346 --> 00:07:54.098 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>AKOREM: so they could communicate with me.</c.bg_transparent>

100
00:07:55.183 --> 00:07:57.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You spoke to them?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I didn't have to.</c.bg_transparent>

101
00:07:57.935 --> 00:08:00.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could sense</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>their understanding, their grace.</c.bg_transparent>

102
00:08:03.524 --> 00:08:06.861 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've never felt such bliss.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>And then they healed me.</c.bg_transparent>

103
00:08:07.403 --> 00:08:11.491 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>A light washed over me,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and then my wound was gone.</c.bg_transparent>

104
00:08:12.909 --> 00:08:16.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>They gave me back my life. I felt reborn.</c.bg_transparent>

105
00:08:17.413 --> 00:08:18.915 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>When exactly did you leave Bajor?</c.bg_transparent>

106
00:08:20.625 --> 00:08:23.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, it couldn't have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>been more than a few days ago.</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:08:23.753 --> 00:08:24.754 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>What was the year?</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:08:25.463 --> 00:08:26.839 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>9174.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:08:31.010 --> 00:08:32.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>That was over 200 years ago.</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:08:34.931 --> 00:08:35.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>200 years?</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:08:40.728 --> 00:08:41.562 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>My wife...</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:08:42.688 --> 00:08:45.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>My parents... they're gone.</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:08:47.318 --> 00:08:49.153 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>BASHIR: If you give us your name,</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:08:49.237 --> 00:08:51.697 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>maybe we can contact your descendants.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:08:51.781 --> 00:08:54.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let them know you're... alive.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:08:55.535 --> 00:09:00.081 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Akorem. Akorem Laan.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>But I have no descendants.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:09:01.415 --> 00:09:04.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My brother died last winter,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and my wife and I never had children.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:09:05.086 --> 00:09:07.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Akorem Laan, the poet?</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:09:08.005 --> 00:09:09.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm a poet, yes.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:09:09.799 --> 00:09:13.636 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You wrote </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Kitara's Song</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>The Call of the Prophets?</i></c.bg_transparent>

121
00:09:15.221 --> 00:09:16.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know my work?</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:09:18.391 --> 00:09:20.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're considered one of the greatest</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>poets of Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:09:21.477 --> 00:09:25.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Every schoolchild can recite</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Gaudaal's Lament </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>from memory.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:09:25.731 --> 00:09:28.276 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>People still read my work,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>after all this time?</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:09:30.111 --> 00:09:33.447 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps, that's part</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the Prophets' plan for me.</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:09:34.448 --> 00:09:35.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Their plan?</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:09:35.825 --> 00:09:38.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not clear to me yet</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>why they made me their Emissary,</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:09:39.203 --> 00:09:41.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I know they gave me back</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>my life for a reason.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:09:41.914 --> 00:09:45.876 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Akorem, a great deal has happened</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>since you've been gone.</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:09:46.961 --> 00:09:50.131 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe Major Kira can spend</c.bg_transparent>
