132
00:09:54.552 --> 00:09:55.386 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's right.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:09:56.095 --> 00:09:58.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But your family would be part</c.bg_transparent>
