00:09:59.181 --> 00:10:00.266 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarra?</i></c.bg_transparent>

135
00:10:02.727 --> 00:10:04.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bajor used to have a strict caste system.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:10:04.895 --> 00:10:07.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A person's work was dictated</c.bg_transparent>
