140
00:10:18.659 --> 00:10:19.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We all became soldiers.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:10:20.953 --> 00:10:22.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Cardassians occupied Bajor?</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:10:23.831 --> 00:10:24.749 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For over 50 years.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:10:28.586 --> 00:10:30.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It seems you're right, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:10:30.421 --> 00:10:33.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A great deal has happened</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>since I've been gone.</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:10:41.724 --> 00:10:43.934 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you look at the prophecies</c.bg_transparent>
