00:10:47.521 --> 00:10:48.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Really?</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:10:48.564 --> 00:10:51.734 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
