151
00:10:56.656 --> 00:10:59.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that there, the Prophets would give</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>him back his life.</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:11:00.076 --> 00:11:00.910 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go on.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:11:01.577 --> 00:11:03.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They didn't give me back my life.</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:11:04.872 --> 00:11:07.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not literally, but they did help you</c.bg_transparent>
