00:11:35.194 --> 00:11:36.070 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's Bajoran.</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:11:36.445 --> 00:11:41.784 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's a revered poet, and he wants the job.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Besides, Starfleet will be thrilled.</c.bg_transparent>

167
