173
00:11:59.885 --> 00:12:01.053 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How does it feel?</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:12:01.595 --> 00:12:04.223 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It feels, uh... good.</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:12:05.224 --> 00:12:06.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No more ceremonies to attend.</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:12:07.435 --> 00:12:08.519 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
