180
00:12:20.865 --> 00:12:22.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I feel like I'm on vacation.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:12:30.833 --> 00:12:31.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief!</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:12:32.877 --> 00:12:34.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Congratulations, Dad.</c.bg_transparent>

183
