185
00:12:39.633 --> 00:12:40.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, just one.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:12:41.427 --> 00:12:42.261 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right.</c.bg_transparent>

187
