<c.bg_transparent>Chief O'Brien is having a baby.</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:12:48.559 --> 00:12:50.686 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought your females carried your young.</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:12:51.395 --> 00:12:54.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My wife. My wife is having the baby.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:12:55.483 --> 00:12:56.692 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Congratulations.</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:12:57.568 --> 00:13:00.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I remember when my nephew Nog was a baby.</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:13:00.696 --> 00:13:03.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cutest thing you ever saw.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:13:04.074 --> 00:13:05.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know babies.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:13:05.409 --> 00:13:07.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Every little thing they pick up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>goes straight into their ears.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:13:08.662 --> 00:13:10.998 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I used to love reading to him.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:13:11.540 --> 00:13:16.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, "See Brak acquire.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Acquire, Brak, acquire."</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:13:19.423 --> 00:13:22.009 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
