<c.bg_transparent>Hard to believe, isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:13:25.930 --> 00:13:27.973 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mind you, they do say the second</c.bg_transparent>
