203
00:13:30.267 --> 00:13:33.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and the endless crying</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and the sleepless nights.</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:13:34.021 --> 00:13:35.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Yeah.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Cheers.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:13:36.023 --> 00:13:37.691 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh... cheers.</c.bg_transparent>

206
