<c.bg_transparent>Is something wrong, Chief?</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:13:41.320 --> 00:13:43.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. Nothing at all. I couldn't be happier.</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:13:43.864 --> 00:13:46.075 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>QUARK: Did you hear?</c.bg_transparent>
