<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to.</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:27:55.090 --> 00:27:56.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can Daddy color, too?</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:27:56.341 --> 00:27:57.884 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm coloring.</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:28:24.285 --> 00:28:27.622 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The four-shift rotation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>also seems to be improving performance.</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:28:27.705 --> 00:28:29.374 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Less mistakes due to fatigue.</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:28:29.958 --> 00:28:33.002 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fine. Let's make the change permanent.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Anything else?</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:28:36.172 --> 00:28:38.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was wondering if, in the next few days</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:28:38.591 --> 00:28:41.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you would have the time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to meet with Major Jatarn.</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:28:42.095 --> 00:28:43.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sure.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:28:45.807 --> 00:28:46.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is something wrong, sir?</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:28:48.560 --> 00:28:49.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:28:50.478 --> 00:28:53.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just received a communiqué</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from Starfleet Command</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:28:53.648 --> 00:28:55.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>responding to my report</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the Bajoran situation.</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:28:56.776 --> 00:28:57.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That bad?</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:28:57.777 --> 00:28:58.737 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not yet,</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:28:59.571 --> 00:29:01.281 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I can read between the lines.</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:29:04.325 --> 00:29:08.163 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was sent here</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to help bring Bajor into the Federation.</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:29:08.955 --> 00:29:11.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That doesn't look like much</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of a possibility anymore.</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:29:11.541 --> 00:29:13.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As far as Starfleet is concerned,</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:29:13.376 --> 00:29:14.836 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have failed my mission.</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:29:15.920 --> 00:29:18.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's not fair. It's not your fault.</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:29:19.758 --> 00:29:21.301 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is from where they're sitting.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:29:22.594 --> 00:29:26.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The irony is, Starfleet was always trying</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:29:26.222 --> 00:29:29.017 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to get me to distance myself</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from this Emissary business.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:29:29.100 --> 00:29:30.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And now that I have...</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:29:35.440 --> 00:29:37.567 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe I could talk</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to First Minister Shakaar</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:29:37.650 --> 00:29:39.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>about sending Starfleet</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a communiqué explai--</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:29:39.861 --> 00:29:42.197 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Thanks.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It--it'll blow over.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:29:43.406 --> 00:29:44.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not that.</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:29:46.493 --> 00:29:48.077 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess I'm just feeling...</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:29:49.913 --> 00:29:50.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I did fail.</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:29:52.582 --> 00:29:53.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir...</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:29:53.792 --> 00:29:58.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Anyway, why did you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>want me to meet Jatarn?</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:29:59.547 --> 00:30:00.381 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:30:02.050 --> 00:30:03.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We can talk about that another time.</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:30:03.927 --> 00:30:04.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What is it, Major?</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:30:07.305 --> 00:30:09.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think he'd make an excellent</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>First Officer.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:30:11.559 --> 00:30:13.436 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As soon as you can find someone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to take my post,</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:30:13.561 --> 00:30:15.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to resign my commission.</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:30:16.439 --> 00:30:17.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:30:17.357 --> 00:30:19.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To follow your...</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> D'jarra.</i></c.bg_transparent>

457
00:30:21.611 --> 00:30:23.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm planning to move back</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Dahkur Province.</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:30:23.822 --> 00:30:25.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are a lot of artists</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who live in the capital,</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:30:26.407 --> 00:30:28.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I have a friend there who's willing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to apprentice me.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:30:31.246 --> 00:30:32.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:30:33.998 --> 00:30:37.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The last thing I want to do is to add</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to your problems.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:30:40.630 --> 00:30:42.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is something I have to do.</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:30:46.678 --> 00:30:48.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sniffles )</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:30:50.306 --> 00:30:51.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If, um...</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:30:52.892 --> 00:30:55.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you don't hit it off</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with Major Jatarn, um,</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:30:55.186 --> 00:30:57.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can think of a few other people.</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:30:57.313 --> 00:30:59.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It shouldn't be that hard to find someone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to replace me.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:31:00.650 --> 00:31:04.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't doubt that I can find</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>someone to fill your post...</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:31:07.448 --> 00:31:09.075 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But to replace you?</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:31:16.374 --> 00:31:19.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door opens, closes )</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:31:25.967 --> 00:31:27.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, time.</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:31:27.635 --> 00:31:30.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>1921 hours.</i></c.bg_transparent>

473
00:31:30.138 --> 00:31:31.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where's Dr. Bashir?</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:31:31.639 --> 00:31:33.892 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Dr. Bashir is in Quark's bar.</i></c.bg_transparent>

475
00:31:40.773 --> 00:31:43.067 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I'm chasing a triple 17</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and a bull, Morn.</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:31:43.234 --> 00:31:44.569 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Got some catching up to do.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:31:44.777 --> 00:31:45.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief!</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:31:48.531 --> 00:31:49.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Excuse me.</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:31:54.370 --> 00:31:55.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:31:55.663 --> 00:31:56.789 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How have you been?</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:31:56.873 --> 00:31:58.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not bad. You?</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:31:58.333 --> 00:32:00.001 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, you know, all right.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:32:00.710 --> 00:32:03.379 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was heading home.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Thought I'd stop in for a quick pint.</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:32:07.634 --> 00:32:08.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:32:08.843 --> 00:32:09.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's been a while, eh?</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:32:10.053 --> 00:32:12.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ha. Seems like weeks.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:32:13.222 --> 00:32:14.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see you found someone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to play darts with.</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:32:14.807 --> 00:32:15.642 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, uh...</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:32:16.267 --> 00:32:18.811 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've set a board up in our quarters</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>so Molly and I can play.</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:32:19.270 --> 00:32:21.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, Morn's, um... he's pretty good.</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:32:21.189 --> 00:32:22.231 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So's Molly.</c.bg_transparent>

492
00:32:23.524 --> 00:32:25.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-It's not the same.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It's not the same.</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:32:29.530 --> 00:32:34.035 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I mean, Molly's just a kid.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You know, we've been playing with magnets.</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:32:34.327 --> 00:32:37.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn couldn't hit a Yridian yak</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at five paces.</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:32:39.165 --> 00:32:40.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We were evenly matched.</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:32:40.750 --> 00:32:41.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We had a good rivalry going on.</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:32:42.043 --> 00:32:43.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeah, kept us sharp.</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:32:43.378 --> 00:32:44.379 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Exactly.</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:32:45.713 --> 00:32:46.547 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're late.</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:32:48.591 --> 00:32:49.509 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you mean?</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:32:50.385 --> 00:32:53.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's Thursday, and I've got your usual</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>holosuite reserved.</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:32:53.513 --> 00:32:54.597 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Didn't you cancel?</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:32:54.681 --> 00:32:56.975 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Actually, I was, um, hoping maybe...</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:32:58.059 --> 00:33:00.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, no, I--I--I got to get home.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:33:01.354 --> 00:33:03.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What about you, Doctor?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The Battle of Britain awaits.</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:33:04.399 --> 00:33:07.110 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you know my policy on cancellations,</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:33:07.735 --> 00:33:09.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>no refunds.</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:33:09.487 --> 00:33:10.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:33:10.863 --> 00:33:14.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe Morn's better in the cockpit</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of a spitfire than he is at darts.</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:33:14.742 --> 00:33:16.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, it wouldn't be the same.</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:33:16.703 --> 00:33:19.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Um... You're right.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:33:20.415 --> 00:33:23.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn probably doesn't even know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>where England is.</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:33:24.043 --> 00:33:25.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughs )</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:33:27.422 --> 00:33:28.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll see you.</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:33:39.100 --> 00:33:40.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Odo to Sisko.</i></c.bg_transparent>

516
00:33:40.935 --> 00:33:41.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:33:42.103 --> 00:33:44.689 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>You'd better come down to the Promenade.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Someone's been killed.</i></c.bg_transparent>

518
00:33:48.943 --> 00:33:50.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What happened?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-We don't know yet.</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:33:50.528 --> 00:33:53.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He fell from the second level.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>His neck was broken on impact.</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:33:53.614 --> 00:33:56.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Did anyone see it happen?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I did.</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:33:58.119 --> 00:33:59.328 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Was it an accident?</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:34:00.163 --> 00:34:01.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I pushed him.</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:34:02.790 --> 00:34:07.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>His family name is Imutta.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Their </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarra </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>is unclean.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:34:08.463 --> 00:34:10.131 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They prepare the dead for burial.</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:34:10.381 --> 00:34:14.469 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I asked him to set the proper example</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and resign from our order.</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:34:14.969 --> 00:34:16.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He refused.</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:34:16.137 --> 00:34:18.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You killed him because of his </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarra?</i></c.bg_transparent>

528
00:34:19.098 --> 00:34:23.853 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had to. If a Vedek can't do</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what the Emissary has asked of us,</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:34:23.936 --> 00:34:25.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>how can we expect anyone else to?</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:34:26.647 --> 00:34:27.982 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get him out of here.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:34:39.368 --> 00:34:40.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I regret what happened here today</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:34:40.995 --> 00:34:44.749 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>as much as you do,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but change is never easy.</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:34:45.833 --> 00:34:47.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The road that the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have asked us to walk</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:34:47.502 --> 00:34:49.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>won't always be a smooth one.</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:34:49.295 --> 00:34:51.756 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And forcing people to follow</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>their </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras</i></c.bg_transparent>

536
00:34:51.839 --> 00:34:53.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>won't make it any smoother.</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:34:53.716 --> 00:34:56.094 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What happened on the Promenade</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was just the beginning.</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:34:56.636 --> 00:34:58.012 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Must I remind you, Captain?</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:34:58.846 --> 00:35:01.099 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm merely fulfilling</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the will of the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:35:01.557 --> 00:35:03.059 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do you know that?</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:35:04.602 --> 00:35:06.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm the Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:35:06.729 --> 00:35:08.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And what you've done with the position</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:35:08.564 --> 00:35:10.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>has made me wish I had never given it up.</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:35:11.109 --> 00:35:13.986 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But you did,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and it was the right decision.</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:35:14.779 --> 00:35:17.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You never truly accepted</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the role in the first place.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:35:20.409 --> 00:35:22.036 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm willing to accept it now.</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:35:26.040 --> 00:35:27.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're challenging my claim.</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:35:28.209 --> 00:35:29.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've left me no choice.</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:35:32.296 --> 00:35:33.965 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If we went to the people</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:35:34.382 --> 00:35:37.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and asked them to choose</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>between us, it would be chaos.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:35:37.468 --> 00:35:40.096 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to divide Bajor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>any more than you do.</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:35:40.680 --> 00:35:42.390 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It wouldn't be divided for long</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:35:42.473 --> 00:35:44.475 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>because in the end,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the people would choose me.</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:35:45.059 --> 00:35:47.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My claim was foretold</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the ancient texts.</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:35:48.688 --> 00:35:53.609 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was the first to find the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I was the first to be with the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:35:54.402 --> 00:35:56.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They gave me back my life.</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:35:56.279 --> 00:35:59.490 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're not going to settle</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this by arguing over ancient texts.</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:36:00.324 --> 00:36:01.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then how?</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:36:01.826 --> 00:36:05.204 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's only one way to be sure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>which one of us is the Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:36:06.622 --> 00:36:09.584 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have to go to the wormhole</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and ask the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:36:31.230 --> 00:36:32.899 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Going to half thrusters.</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:36:34.400 --> 00:36:35.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:36:38.696 --> 00:36:39.655 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now what?</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:36:40.781 --> 00:36:41.616 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We wait.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:37:08.017 --> 00:37:11.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( thudding heartbeat )</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:37:11.312 --> 00:37:13.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You are the Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:37:13.564 --> 00:37:15.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is the one that was injured.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:37:15.983 --> 00:37:19.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, I was. And you gave me back my life,</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:37:19.862 --> 00:37:21.906 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>just as the texts foretold.</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:37:21.989 --> 00:37:23.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why are you here?</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:37:23.991 --> 00:37:27.578 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To... prove to this nonbeliever</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:37:27.662 --> 00:37:31.624 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that you sent me to put Bajor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>back on the right path.</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:37:32.416 --> 00:37:36.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please, tell him you chose me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be the Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:37:36.963 --> 00:37:40.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell that him that I fulfilled</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the ancient prophecies,</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:37:40.883 --> 00:37:43.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that I was the first to find</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Celestial Temple.</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:37:43.761 --> 00:37:47.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was the first to meet with you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He came to you centuries later.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:37:48.474 --> 00:37:49.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>First...</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:37:50.851 --> 00:37:51.686 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Later...</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:37:52.770 --> 00:37:55.231 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They have no meaning to us.</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:37:55.898 --> 00:37:58.067 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: The Bajorans believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you are their Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:37:58.150 --> 00:38:00.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That you have chosen</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>one of us to be your Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:38:07.285 --> 00:38:10.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We... are of Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:38:11.080 --> 00:38:12.039 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go on.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:38:17.336 --> 00:38:19.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They are linear.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:38:19.130 --> 00:38:20.965 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It limits them.</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:38:21.507 --> 00:38:23.509 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They do not understand.</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:38:23.592 --> 00:38:25.761 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But we want to understand.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:38:26.387 --> 00:38:27.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's why we're here.</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:38:28.347 --> 00:38:30.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You saved his life. Why?</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:38:30.433 --> 00:38:32.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was injured.</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:38:33.102 --> 00:38:34.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We kept him with us.</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:38:34.353 --> 00:38:36.605 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So that I would be spared the occupation.</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:38:36.689 --> 00:38:39.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So that I could bring</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>back to Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:38:39.525 --> 00:38:41.110 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that true?</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:38:41.402 --> 00:38:43.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that what you want?</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:38:43.904 --> 00:38:48.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>are part of what the Sisko</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>would call the past.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:38:48.868 --> 00:38:53.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Sisko taught us that for you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what was can never be again.</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:38:53.622 --> 00:38:57.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> belong in the past,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>why did you send me into the future?</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:39:01.672 --> 00:39:02.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For the Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:39:04.550 --> 00:39:06.469 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For me?</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:39:07.136 --> 00:39:09.347 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're saying that he's your Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:39:10.890 --> 00:39:12.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He is the Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:39:15.895 --> 00:39:18.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then I've been wrong...</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:39:18.272 --> 00:39:19.398 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>About everything.</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:39:21.192 --> 00:39:23.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You should have let me die.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:39:24.028 --> 00:39:25.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We still can.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:39:27.031 --> 00:39:28.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We can return him</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:39:28.532 --> 00:39:30.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to the moment we found him.</c.bg_transparent>

609
00:39:31.577 --> 00:39:33.245 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Allow him to die.</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:39:33.329 --> 00:39:34.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:39:35.247 --> 00:39:37.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why not return him to his own time</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:39:38.084 --> 00:39:44.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>as he is now, uninjured,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>so that he can get back safely to Bajor?</c.bg_transparent>

613
00:39:48.886 --> 00:39:52.390 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He would remember</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>nothing of what has happened.</c.bg_transparent>

614
00:39:53.891 --> 00:39:57.061 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could be with my wife and family.</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:40:02.191 --> 00:40:03.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm ready to go home.</c.bg_transparent>

616
00:40:05.653 --> 00:40:06.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why?</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:40:08.114 --> 00:40:09.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why do you stay here?</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:40:09.782 --> 00:40:11.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because I still have questions.</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:40:13.661 --> 00:40:15.704 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We are of Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:40:16.622 --> 00:40:18.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What does that mean?</c.bg_transparent>

621
00:40:19.250 --> 00:40:22.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>You... </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>are of Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:40:51.323 --> 00:40:53.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, Molly really loves</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that book Jake gave her.</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:40:53.784 --> 00:40:56.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She made me read it to her three times</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>before she fell asleep.</c.bg_transparent>

624
00:41:01.917 --> 00:41:02.751 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:41:03.586 --> 00:41:05.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to be working another few hours.</c.bg_transparent>

626
00:41:05.713 --> 00:41:09.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Well, that's okay.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'll, uh... I'll read.</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:41:10.259 --> 00:41:11.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you want to go do something...</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:41:12.094 --> 00:41:14.263 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. I'm fine.</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:41:19.560 --> 00:41:20.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:41:21.770 --> 00:41:27.735 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Miles, I promised I wouldn't say anything,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but it's about Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:41:29.236 --> 00:41:30.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What about him?</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:41:31.363 --> 00:41:34.283 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I ran into him the other day,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and he seemed depressed.</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:41:34.366 --> 00:41:37.036 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'd never admit it,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but he really misses you.</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:41:37.578 --> 00:41:38.412 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Poor guy.</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:41:39.288 --> 00:41:41.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No family to come home to every night.</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:41:42.333 --> 00:41:45.002 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe you should go find him.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You know, cheer him up a little.</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:41:46.712 --> 00:41:48.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Depressed, is he?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Very.</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:41:49.131 --> 00:41:50.549 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe I should go spend an hour with him.</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:41:51.008 --> 00:41:51.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe two.</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:41:58.682 --> 00:41:59.892 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm a lucky man.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:42:05.064 --> 00:42:06.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Keiko to Dr. Bashir.</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:42:06.941 --> 00:42:07.983 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Go ahead.</i></c.bg_transparent>

643
00:42:08.400 --> 00:42:10.069 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Julian, it's about Miles.</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:42:10.152 --> 00:42:14.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I promised I wouldn't tell anyone,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>but he's been really depressed lately.</i></c.bg_transparent>

645
00:42:15.950 --> 00:42:16.867 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh.</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:42:23.541 --> 00:42:24.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want you to have this.</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:42:24.750 --> 00:42:28.921 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's an original Kira Nerys.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It could be very valuable one day.</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:42:29.838 --> 00:42:31.257 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hear she didn't make many.</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:42:31.757 --> 00:42:33.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( both laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:42:36.011 --> 00:42:38.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought your speech</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>went very well yesterday.</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:42:38.556 --> 00:42:40.391 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was the right thing to do.</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:42:40.766 --> 00:42:43.394 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wanted everyone to know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what happened to Akorem</c.bg_transparent>

653
00:42:43.477 --> 00:42:47.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and that the Prophets said nothing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about returning to the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras.</i></c.bg_transparent>

654
00:42:47.940 --> 00:42:49.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just about everyone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was relieved to hear it.</c.bg_transparent>

655
00:42:50.025 --> 00:42:52.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-It's your own fault.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I can't believe you didn't cover me.</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:42:52.361 --> 00:42:54.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How was I to know you were going to insult</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the King of Leinster?</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:42:54.905 --> 00:42:56.323 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Ah!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-In his own keep!</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:42:56.407 --> 00:42:57.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:42:58.075 --> 00:43:01.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was just reading one of Akorem's poems,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>The Call of the Prophets.</i></c.bg_transparent>

660
00:43:01.912 --> 00:43:03.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, that's one of my favorites.</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:43:03.831 --> 00:43:05.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a shame he never finished it.</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:43:05.916 --> 00:43:07.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He did. Look.</c.bg_transparent>

663
00:43:11.380 --> 00:43:12.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is confusing.</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:43:14.300 --> 00:43:18.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The last time I read this poem,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it ended after the 12th stanza.</c.bg_transparent>

665
00:43:19.013 --> 00:43:20.806 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If the timeline's been changed,</c.bg_transparent>

666
00:43:21.849 --> 00:43:24.059 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>then why do I remember things</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the way they used to be?</c.bg_transparent>

667
00:43:24.643 --> 00:43:27.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets work in mysterious ways.</c.bg_transparent>

668
00:43:29.815 --> 00:43:30.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MALE: Excuse me, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

669
00:43:31.191 --> 00:43:32.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes?</c.bg_transparent>

670
00:43:32.276 --> 00:43:36.739 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sorry to bother you, but tomorrow</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>after evening services in the Temple,</c.bg_transparent>

671
00:43:36.822 --> 00:43:39.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>we're having my daughter's</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i></i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>ih'tanu </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>ceremony.</c.bg_transparent>

672
00:43:41.076 --> 00:43:42.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She's turning 14.</c.bg_transparent>

673
00:43:43.078 --> 00:43:44.204 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Happy birthday.</c.bg_transparent>

674
00:43:45.456 --> 00:43:49.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We were wondering if there's any chance</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you could come and give her your blessing.</c.bg_transparent>

675
00:43:50.044 --> 00:43:51.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It would mean so much to us.</c.bg_transparent>

676
00:43:52.212 --> 00:43:53.297 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd be happy to.</c.bg_transparent>

677
00:43:55.424 --> 00:43:56.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you, Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

678
00:43:57.676 --> 00:43:58.636 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're welcome.</c.bg_transparent>

